Appointment#status_update

Appointment Status Update
=========================

Hello <%= @customer_name %>,

There's an update on your appointment (Ref: <%= @appointment.appointment_number %>) with <%= @company.name %> scheduled for <%= @appointment.appointment_date.strftime("%a, %b %d, %Y at %I:%M %p") %>.

The new status is: <%= @status.capitalize %>

You can view the details here:
<%= @status_url %>

Thank you!